2:T73a,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is BrightEdge better than SE Ranking?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. BrightEdge scores 8.0 overall while SE Ranking scores 8.0. BrightEdge is best for Fortune 500 companies and enterprise marketing, while SE Ranking excels for small agencies and freelancers."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, BrightEdge or SE Ranking?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"BrightEdge starts at Custom and SE Ranking starts at $65/mo.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from BrightEdge to SE Ranking?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both BrightEdge and SE Ranking support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about BrightEdge vs SE Ranking?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, BrightEdge holds an overall rating of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 5/10. SE Ranking has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise BrightEdge for industry-leading enterprise seo platform and SE Ranking for excellent value for an all-in-one tool."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, BrightEdge or SE Ranking?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend BrightEdge for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, SE Ranking remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize excellent value for an all-in-one tool. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTM